Package com.github.tadukoo.junit.constant

Interface DefaultTestValues

All Known Implementing Classes:
MappedPojoTest, PojoTest
public interface DefaultTestValues
Default values to use for testing, so we can have them consistent between the JUnit tests and the actual source assertions
Version:
Alpha v.0.1
Author:
Logan Ferree (Tadukoo)
